        <abstract>
            <p>Sends blood of pigeons for examination. Discusses variation of blood in related animals.</p> 
<p>Would like copy of book edited by GG [<hi rend="italic">The works of W. Hewson</hi> (1846)].</p> 
            <p>Suggests investigation of blood in varieties of domesticated animals.</p>
        </abstract>
